        <li><a href="/guides/damariscotta-dispensary-guide">Damariscotta Dispensary Guide</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="faq-section">
    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <Faq
      questions={[
        { q: "Are there cannabis dispensaries in Boothbay, Maine?", a: "Yes. HIGHLY Cannaco operates a recreational dispensary at 638 Wiscasset Rd, Boothbay. Founded 2017, expanded to adult-use 2021, now with 7 locations statewide. Phone: (207) 315-6719." },
        { q: "What makes HIGHLY Cannaco Boothbay unique?", a: "HIGHLY Cannaco Boothbay features a live viewing window into the grow room, in-house living soil cultivation, and a seven-location statewide network. Their daily deals rotate by product category." },
        { q: "Where can I buy medical cannabis near Boothbay?", a: "Bayside Bud Shack in Northport (~20 mi north) serves both medical and recreational. Rockland has Scrimshaw Cannabis (medical) ~15 mi northeast." },
      ]}
    />
  </section>

  <p class="disclaimer"><strong>Disclaimer:</strong> Information is provided for general reference only. Dispensary hours, product availability, and policies can change. Always verify details directly with the dispensary before planning a visit.</p>
</article>
